********************************************************************************
3rd party graphics - free
********************************************************************************
Logo font is based off Audiowide
* Copyright (c) 2012, Brian J. Bonislawsky DBA Astigmatic (AOETI)
* SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1

Dialog & menu font is based off Deathwake font by Zee-3
* http://www.zee-3.com/pickfordbros/archive/bitmapfonts.php
* "Feel free to use any of these fonts for whatever purpose you see fit."

********************************************************************************
3rd party graphics - commercial
********************************************************************************
Almost all of the graphics are based off the following licensed tilesets:
* Modern exteriors: https://limezu.itch.io/modernexteriors
* Modern interiors: https://limezu.itch.io/moderninteriors
* Modern office: https://limezu.itch.io/modernoffice
* Modern UI: https://limezu.itch.io/modernuserinterface
All three were created by LimeZu (https://limezu.itch.io/)

Some graphics are from the GameDev Market 8Bit/Pixelart Humble Bundle
* https://www.humblebundle.com/software/8bit-pixel-game-dev-software
* https://www.gamedevmarket.net/terms-conditions/#pro-licence

The night sky on the title screen is from the Pixel Art Infinite Runner Pack
* https://edermunizz.itch.io/infinite-runner

If you want to use any of these in a project please purchase a license. 
These are all inexpensive sets so just do it.
 
********************************************************************************
Physical Redistribution
******************************************************************************** 
I can't stop anyone from making physical reproductions of this game but would
really prefer they didn't. This is a free game and I'd like to keep it that way.

